    %div{ style: 'padding: 15px 30px; color: #888; font-size: .9em; text-align: center; background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #CCC; border-top: 1px solid #E7E7E7; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; line-height: 1.4em;' }
      You are receiving e-mail notifications from Syme. <br />
      You can
      %a{ href: "http://www.getsyme.com/unsubscribe/#{locals[:recipient]}/#{locals[:unsubscribe_token]}", target: '_blank' } unsubscribe
      from these emails at any time.

